{"tid":822175,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★高鐵西九巴士站首日啟用，沒有巴士夠膽駛入車站 警鐘長響","createTime":"2018-09-16T08:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T09:45:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb9775598396a93e81463568bb807b14d8e82720","tid":822175,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:04:27.000Z","msg":"強颱風「山竹」不單吹得港人頭都痛，也壞了一場好事。本應今日啟用的高鐵西九龍站巴士總站，因為八號風球已經於清晨懸掛關係，至今<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有一架巴士夠膽駛入車站；站內警報鐘聲一直長響</span>，在場的工人表示是因為風力太強，「吹到佢響。」<br />\n<br />\n西九龍巴士總站啟用後，會有11條巴士線遷入，不過因為颱風關係，車站啟用後沒有巴士停泊。站內的車長休息室亦已關好門，及貼上牛皮膠紙。<br />\n現場有數名工人在休息，其中一人表示，至今沒有行人路過，相信原因是接駁巴士站至港鐵站的天橋仍未啟用有關。<br />\n<br />\n九巴早前表示，站內沒有洗手間，其後運輸署發稿還擊指，是設有洗手間的。但記者現場所見，洗手間是設於站外地方，由站頭行去，有近200米距離。而廁所也受風暴吹襲，滿地樹葉，滿目瘡痍。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵柯士甸站前往高鐵西九站的出口水浸，有工人在場施工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180916/large/1537084044_2154.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180916%2Flarge%2F1537084044_2154.jpg&h=8689efe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180916/58688505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F58688505&d=yzDWzY8%2F1k9pWZDPZiwDOpUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=b416cb70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F58688505&h=6cbd6e66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180916/58688505</a>"},{"pid":"af0a7ba2cc8c03db4bdd55c6278694893ef5de46","tid":822175,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b616e6ea60d779b3503c5d37d0927d9aeee8caa0","tid":822175,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"af0a7ba2cc8c03db